# Flutter Testing

## Running Tests
- Use `flutter test` (or `run_tests` tool if available)

## Patterns
- **AAA**: Arrange-Act-Assert (Given-When-Then)
- Unit tests: domain logic, data layer, state management
- Widget tests: UI components
- Integration tests: end-to-end flows via `integration_test` package

## Mocks
- Prefer fakes/stubs over mocks
- Use `mockito` or `mocktail` when mocks are needed
- Avoid code generation for mocks when possible

## Coverage
- Aim for high test coverage
- Prefer `package:checks` for assertions when available
